 
<p>
Artificial imitation grass is <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2022/jul/17/why-fake-grass-is-far-from-green-in-ways-you-might-not-guess">bad for the environment and for
wildlife</a>, requires time-consuming maintenance, and gets much hotter
than real grass.  And it has to be watered (washed).

 